itle = \n |DirectedBy      = \n |WrittenBy       = \n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2020|5|7}}\n |Viewers         = \n |ShortSummary    = \n |LineColor       = 000000\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber   = 64\n |EpisodeNumber2  = 8\n |Title           = \n |RTitle = \n |DirectedBy      = \n |WrittenBy       = \n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2020|5|14}}\n |Viewers         = \n |ShortSummary    = \n |LineColor       = 000000\n}}-->\n}}\nOther episodes of the fourth season include:<ref name=\"WGA\">{{Cite web |url=https://directories.wga.org/project/1115009/man-with-a-plan/ |title=Man with a Plan |website=[[Writers Guild of America West]] |access-date=February 22, 2020}} Episodes with a credit date in 2019.</ref>\n<!--Do NOT add to the episodes table until it has been confirmed by episode numbers with a reliable source or the episodes have been released!-->\n* \"Happy Ann-RV-sary\" written by Mark Gross\n* \"Stuck in the Middle with You\" written by Jessica Runck\n* \"Full Metal Teddy\" written by John Jack O'Brien\n* \"Adam's Not Sorry\" written by [[Tommy Johnagin]]\n* \"Dude, Where's My Boat?\" written by Farhan Arshad\n\n==Ratings==\n{{Television ratings graph\n| title       = Man with a Plan\n| country     = U.S.\n| color1      = #10519C\n| color2      = #72BBE6\n| color3      = #9F3302\n| color4      = #000000\n| x_intervals = 5\n| y_intervals = 200\n| bar_width   = 13\n| average     = y\n| refs        = <ref>For the first season, see {{cite web |url=https://tvseriesfinale.com/tv-show/man-with-a-plan-cbs-tv-show-season-one-ratings/|title=Man with a Plan: Season One Ratings|work=TV Series Finale|date=May 16, 2017|accessdate=April 9, 2020|url-status=live}}\n----\nFor the second season, see {{cite web |url=https://tvseriesfinale.com/tv-show/man-plan-season-two-ratings/|title=Man with a Plan: Season Two Ratings|work=TV Series Finale|date=May 22, 2018|accessdate=April 9, 2020|url-status=live}}\n----\nFor the third season, see {{cite web |url=https://tvseriesfina